    "description": "Para Bellum - Hold the Line is a 3D real time small unit tactics game. Your task is to hold off enemy attacks wave after wave using a variety of different Units and Supports in your arsenal to the best of your abilities in Campaign and Skirmish modes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/058943e52c0c469c76478e62607a4434.poster.avif?t=1649329761\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/058943e52c0c469c76478e62607a4434.webm?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/058943e52c0c469c76478e62607a4434.mp4?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>UNITS</strong><br>Deploy and order a multitude of different Units including Riflemen, Medics, Machinegunners and Anti-Vehicle Infantry.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/4544626159fdea0b38e8bc90ad533a26.poster.avif?t=1649329761\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/4544626159fdea0b38e8bc90ad533a26.webm?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/4544626159fdea0b38e8bc90ad533a26.mp4?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SUPPORTS</strong><br>Turn the tide of the battle by calling in support in the forms of Mortar or Air Strikes, Supply Drops and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/d85c1e93ebc5f2134e69ddb1b7448ddb.poster.avif?t=1649329761\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/d85c1e93ebc5f2134e69ddb1b7448ddb.webm?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/d85c1e93ebc5f2134e69ddb1b7448ddb.mp4?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>CAMPAIGN</strong><br>Complete a campaign of 15 unique missions. Units that survive a battle will gain experience and accompany you to your next mission, but be aware - if they get killed, they're lost forever!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/d9e56fa4b0f2fe0a83e726aa7e739c19.poster.avif?t=1649329761\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/d9e56fa4b0f2fe0a83e726aa7e739c19.webm?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/d9e56fa4b0f2fe0a83e726aa7e739c19.mp4?t=1649329761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>PLATOON</strong><br>Customize your Platoon by requesting new types of Units and Supports. This will help you gain the upper hand in the battlefield.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/9fc8eec7c196e05f2e0c52fda0ebe48b.avif?t=1649329761\" width=540 height=304 /></span><br><br><strong>SKIRMISH</strong><br>Skirmish mode allows you to play any of the game's maps with customizable settings.",
